data.description: Discover the charm of this ~1,871 sq ft, 3-bedroom, 2-full bathroom single-level home sitting on 5 riverfront acres. Hardwood flooring running throughout the space with gas stone fireplace in the second living room and natural flow to the dining room and kitchen. The kitchen offers ample storage along with gas stove, and leads to a Trex porch. Primary bedroom includes an ensuite bath with walk in closet with additional bedroom and full bath and office space wraps up the inside of the home. Outside is complete with attached 2 car garage with automatic dog door and 3-car detached shop (both heated), two carports, outbuildings, fruit trees, fully fenced back yard, poured concrete patio, and a river bar with firepit. This property has it all!
